sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Controller Manager
    participant ExtUser as External User
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Database as External Database

    Note over User,Operator: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token/Client Cert
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Services,<br/>Route, PVC, ServiceMonitor, SA<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created

    Note over ExtUser,TrustyAI: Flow 2: External User Access
    ExtUser->>Router: HTTPS request to Route<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Re-encrypt to OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth Session Cookie/Bearer
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth token
    OAuth->>TrustyAI: Forward to service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    TrustyAI-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>ExtUser: JSON Response

    Note over Prometheus,TrustyAI: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics (trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)

    Note over Operator,TrustyAI: Flow 4: KServe InferenceService Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceServices<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService events
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch ModelMesh Deployments<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS env var<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Deployment patched
    Note over TrustyAI: ModelMesh pods send inference<br/>payloads to TrustyAI for monitoring

    Note over TrustyAI,Database: Flow 5: Database Storage Mode
    TrustyAI->>Database: JDBC Connection<br/>Varies/TCP<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+ (optional)<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    Database-->>TrustyAI: Data persisted
